Programming Languages (cs.PL) is another possible category as it involves designing a language. Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) is also a possibility as it deals with automated reasoning. Lastly, Machine Learning (cs.LG) could be a potential category as it involves transferring expertise from experienced users to new users.
